 We know that Amy is 5 years older than Jackson and 2 years younger than Corey. This means that Amy is 5 years older than Jackson and 2 years younger than Corey. This also implies that Jackson is 2 years younger than Corey. Since James is 10 and is 1 year younger than Corey, we can infer that Jackson is also 1 year younger than Corey. 

